This module provides an interface to the altlinux hyphenator (derived from libhnj).
The altlinux hyphenator uses modified TeX hyphenation dictionaries. For details, see
the altlinux directory.

Use:

> object h = Public.Tools.Language.Hyphenate("altlinux/hyph_en_US.dic"); 
> h->hyphenate("longfellow");                             
(1) Result: "longfel-low"